DESCRIPTION:Run the regulatory verification cadence:\n\n1. Staleness check:\n   bash /Users/europa/Code/evoked-dev/scripts/verify-regulatory-state.sh --staleness\n\n2. If stale\, copy the verification prompt to clipboard:\n   bash /Users/europa/Code/evoked-dev/scripts/verify-regulatory-state.sh --prompt | pbcopy\n\n3. Paste into a fresh Claude Code session. Claude runs WebSearch + WebFetch and surfaces deltas.\n\n4. Review deltas; update regulatory-state.yml; sweep affected artifacts within 7 days.\n\nSource of truth: src/content/regulatory-state/regulatory-state.yml\nProtocol: src/content/regulatory-state/README.md\n\nFirst occurrence: 2026-06-13 (next_verification_due per state file).\nCadence: weekly during EU AI Act active amendment. Switch to monthly once Official Journal publishes the Digital Omnibus consolidated text.
